data.description: 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with large bonus room that could be used as game, hobby, den or tv room. This property sits on a quarter acre at the end of a cul-de-sac. Recently updated, it boasts fresh paint, tiled floors, dual pane windows, newer HVAC, indoor laundry, modern bath vanities, kitchen offers maple shaker-style cabinets, stainless steel kitchen appliances, updated lighting and more. Plenty of elbow room to entertain outside on the covered patio with mountain views. Have toys? There's no HOA here, so bring them as there is plenty of space in the yard.
